{
  "stem": "15577.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we got panicked with the time because every day which-- when it was late and the women didn't arrived, we were beginning to lose our hopes because, you know, knowing that there were in Auschwitz, we knew what, what may happen in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we began-- 'we,' that means 'the people who were around, surrounding Schindler who were-- who were able to influence Schindler, whom he also believed and wanted them-- he wanted them to influence him.' So these people began to, to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] act and to press on, to make pressure on Schindler.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He should act.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Were these the leaders of the survivors?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "These were the Jewish leaders?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, these were, these were a leader group from our--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From our list, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Four or five people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the main man was Stern.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was the most influential, and he was the man who was kind of real adviser.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we know now-- now we know for sure but we knew even at that time-- that Schindler doesn't make anything without at least letting know Stern and mostly taking advice from Schindler.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Stern.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So he began to, to, to, to ask him to act.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at that time, he, again, what we see of what we saw in the film that Schindler went to Auschwitz and gave diamonds to the commanding officer, this is not the right-- this is not accurate, let's say it this way, because he really bribed them and really settled it but his way.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He sent his mistress to, to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you may imagine that this mistress was a beauty, a real beauty.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he told her he would know it positively.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
